nodes.text: A male Human served as an ensign aboard the New Republic Dauntless-class heavy cruiser Endor. In 13 ABY, the Endor went on a patrol near the planetoid RZ7-6113-23 and intercepted two TIE/sr starfighters. They followed the starfighters until the ensign detected large energy spike coming from the planetoid and warned the captain, who then realized the trap and ordered a withdrawal. The order came too late as the Endor was destroyed by a single blast from the fully charged cannon.
